{"tid":176444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★骨灰龕新條例：骨灰龕位價近月爆升20%","createTime":"2017-03-28T07:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T08:28:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c05a7313aebbaa229aa65c9ae70ba76672557a24","tid":176444,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"新界區一個龕場其中一個正面牆偏正中位置的龕位，兩年前一手售約50萬港元，之後一直未有先人上位，到年初有人放盤，至上月以逾60萬港元成交轉手，同一龕場另一個單人位上月放盤價近70萬港元，持有人本月叫價已升至80萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n由於龕場申領牌照期間或會停售龕位，屆時市場或現一段頗長時間真空期，令龕位炒風近月先吹起。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170328/bkn-20170328070045215-0328_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170328%2Fbkn-20170328070045215-0328_00822_001.html&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=cedef90e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170328/bkn-20170328070045215-0328_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5881fa7d59847118c995c02f34d2d54cc872d3d1","tid":176444,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"別以為自殺就可解決問題，一日在香港，陰陽都要受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1dd3b02d60b10028b6c722118abfa74f575705a","tid":176444,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3a9794179b2078c2f44076a1cbaa4830459461","tid":176444,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"生於香港做窮撚，可能是前世罪孽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e91e00fbbee7e20de152eaf969aae0145be815","t